{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 1,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 339.893,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I, Nephi, having been born of goodly parents,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.431,
      "end": 7.239,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore I was taught somewhat in all the learning of my father;",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.419,
      "end": 11.041,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and having seen many afflictions in the course of my days,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 11.221,
      "end": 15.308,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, having been highly favored of the Lord in all my days;",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 15.488,
      "end": 19.853,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, having had a great knowledge of the goodness and the mysteries of God,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 20.033,
      "end": 23.377,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore I make a record of my proceedings in my days.",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 24.057,
      "end": 27.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, I make a record in the language of my father,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 27.441,
      "end": 30.413,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which consists of the learning of the Jews",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 30.593,
      "end": 33.147,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the language of the Egyptians.",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 33.827,
      "end": 36.706,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I know that the record which I make is true;",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 36.886,
      "end": 38.883,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I make it with mine own hand;",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 39.063,
      "end": 41.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I make it according to my knowledge.",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 41.972,
      "end": 45.687,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For it came to pass in the commencement of the first year",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 45.867,
      "end": 48.793,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of the reign of Zedekiah, king of Judah,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 48.973,
      "end": 53.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "(my father, Lehi, having dwelt at Jerusalem in all his days);",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 53.24,
      "end": 56.398,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in that same year there came many prophets,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 56.578,
      "end": 58.482,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prophesying unto the people",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 58.662,
      "end": 60.195,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they must repent,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 60.375,
      "end": 63.394,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or the great city Jerusalem must be destroyed.",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 64.074,
      "end": 68.532,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore it came to pass that my father, Lehi, as he went forth",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 68.712,
      "end": 70.337,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prayed unto the Lord,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 70.517,
      "end": 72.653,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even with all his heart,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 72.833,
      "end": 74.319,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in behalf of his people.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 74.999,
      "end": 77.971,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass as he prayed unto the Lord,",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 78.151,
      "end": 79.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there came a pillar of fire",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 80.096,
      "end": 82.511,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and dwelt upon a rock before him;",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 82.691,
      "end": 84.827,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he saw and heard much;",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 85.007,
      "end": 88.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and because of the things which he saw and heard",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 88.345,
      "end": 90.574,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he did quake and tremble exceedingly.",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 91.254,
      "end": 95.526,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he returned to his own house at Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 95.706,
      "end": 97.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he cast himself upon his bed,",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 98.115,
      "end": 100.205,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "being overcome with the Spirit",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 100.385,
      "end": 102.568,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the things which he had seen.",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 103.248,
      "end": 105.802,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And being thus overcome with the Spirit,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 105.982,
      "end": 108.304,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he was carried away in a vision,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 108.484,
      "end": 110.852,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even that he saw the heavens open",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 111.032,
      "end": 114.097,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he thought he saw God sitting upon his throne,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 114.277,
      "end": 117.574,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "surrounded with numberless concourses of angels",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 117.754,
      "end": 121.098,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the attitude of singing and praising their God.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 121.778,
      "end": 124.239,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he saw One",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 124.419,
      "end": 126.834,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "descending out of the midst of heaven,",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 127.014,
      "end": 129.568,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he beheld that his luster",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 129.748,
      "end": 132.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was above that of the sun at noon-day.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 132.889,
      "end": 135.443,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also saw twelve others following him,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 135.623,
      "end": 140.267,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their brightness did exceed that of the stars in the firmament.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 140.947,
      "end": 142.665,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they came down",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 142.845,
      "end": 145.492,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and went forth upon the face of the earth;",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 145.672,
      "end": 147.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the first came",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 147.431,
      "end": 149.289,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and stood before my father,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 149.469,
      "end": 151.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and gave unto him a book,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 151.46,
      "end": 153.921,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bade him that he should read.",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 154.601,
      "end": 156.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that as he read,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 157.149,
      "end": 159.471,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he was filled with the Spirit of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 160.151,
      "end": 161.73,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he read, saying:",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 161.91,
      "end": 163.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wo, wo, unto Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 164.04,
      "end": 166.548,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I have seen thine abominations!",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 166.728,
      "end": 170.443,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, and many things did my father read concerning Jerusalem\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 170.623,
      "end": 172.388,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it should be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 172.568,
      "end": 174.518,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the inhabitants thereof;",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 174.698,
      "end": 176.974,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many should perish by the sword,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 177.154,
      "end": 180.405,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and many should be carried away captive into Babylon.",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 181.085,
      "end": 184.707,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when my father had read and seen",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 184.887,
      "end": 187.116,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many great and marvelous things,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 187.296,
      "end": 190.361,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he did exclaim many things unto the Lord; such as:",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 190.541,
      "end": 193.095,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Great and marvelous are thy works,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 193.275,
      "end": 194.947,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord God Almighty!",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 195.127,
      "end": 197.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thy throne is high in the heavens,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 197.49,
      "end": 198.837,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thy power,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 199.017,
      "end": 200.178,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and goodness,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 200.358,
      "end": 201.565,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and mercy",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 201.745,
      "end": 204.346,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are over all the inhabitants of the earth;",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 204.526,
      "end": 206.755,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and, because thou art merciful,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 206.935,
      "end": 211.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thou wilt not suffer those who come unto thee that they shall perish!",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 211.934,
      "end": 214.999,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner was the language of my father",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 215.179,
      "end": 217.129,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the praising of his God;",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 217.309,
      "end": 219.213,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for his soul did rejoice,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 219.393,
      "end": 221.436,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and his whole heart was filled,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 221.616,
      "end": 223.892,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the things which he had seen,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 224.072,
      "end": 226.301,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, which the Lord had shown unto him.",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 226.981,
      "end": 232.275,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, do not make a full account of the things which my father hath written,",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 232.455,
      "end": 234.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he hath written many things",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 235.096,
      "end": 237.604,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he saw in visions and in dreams;",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 237.784,
      "end": 240.71,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he also hath written many things",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 240.89,
      "end": 244.001,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he prophesied and spake unto his children,",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 244.181,
      "end": 246.689,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of which I shall not make a full account.",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 247.369,
      "end": 251.27,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But I shall make an account of my proceedings in my days.",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 251.45,
      "end": 254.794,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I make a abridgment of the record of my father,",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 254.974,
      "end": 258.132,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon plates which I have made with mine own hands;",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 258.312,
      "end": 261.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, after I have abridged the record of my father",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 262.068,
      "end": 264.901,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then will I make an account of mine own life.",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 265.581,
      "end": 267.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore, I would that ye should know",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 268.037,
      "end": 273.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that after the Lord had shown so many marvelous things unto my father, Lehi,",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 273.372,
      "end": 276.019,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, concerning the destruction of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 276.199,
      "end": 278.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold he went forth among the people,",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 278.562,
      "end": 280.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and began to prophesy",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 280.46,
      "end": 285.058,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to declare unto them concerning the things which he had both seen and heard.",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 285.738,
      "end": 289.035,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Jews did mock him",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 289.215,
      "end": 292.373,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the things which he testified of them;",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 292.553,
      "end": 296.779,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he truly testified of their wickedness and their abominations;",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 296.959,
      "end": 300.814,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he testified that the things which he saw and heard,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 300.994,
      "end": 303.873,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the things which he read in the book,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 304.053,
      "end": 307.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "manifested plainly of the coming of a Messiah,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 307.437,
      "end": 309.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the redemption of the world.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 310.3,
      "end": 314.201,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when the Jews heard these things they were angry with him;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 314.381,
      "end": 316.889,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even as with the prophets of old,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 317.069,
      "end": 318.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whom they had cast out,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 319.06,
      "end": 320.825,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and stoned, and slain;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 321.005,
      "end": 322.909,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they also sought his life,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
